theorem Topology.P3_isClosed_implies_isOpen {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    Topology.P3 A → IsClosed A → IsOpen A := by
  intro hP3 hClosed
  have h_subset : A ⊆ interior A := by
    simpa [hClosed.closure_eq] using hP3
  have h_eq : interior A = A := Set.Subset.antisymm interior_subset h_subset
  simpa [h_eq] using (isOpen_interior : IsOpen (interior A))

theorem Topology.closure_interior_eq_of_P1_and_isClosed {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} (hP1 : Topology.P1 A) (hClosed : IsClosed A) :
    closure (interior A) = A := by
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  ·
    have h_subset : interior A ⊆ A := interior_subset
    exact closure_minimal h_subset hClosed
  ·
    exact hP1
